    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Add some flair to your child&#039;s bedroom with the Officially Licensed Fleece Throw Blanket!</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">Cozy 45&quot; x 60&quot; Kids Fleece Throw Blanket Mickey Mouse Paw Patrol Pokemon Soft</h2>\n  <p>Add some flair to your child&#039;s bedroom with the Officially Licensed Fleece Throw Blanket!</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>OFFICIALLY LICENSED - Featuring Favorite Characters from Kid&#039;s Shows and Movies | Great Bedroom Decor for Young Kids</li>\n    <li>SUPER SOFT BLANKET - Made of 100% Polyester to Keep Your Child Warm | Ideal for Travel, Sleepovers, Picnics and More</li>\n    <li>CHILD SIZED - Blanket Measures 45&quot; x 60&quot; (114cm x 152cm) | Perfect Size for Children&#039;s Beds, Playrooms or Family Rooms</li>\n    <li>EASY TO CLEAN - Machine Washable On Cold | Don&#039;t Worry About Occasional Messes or Spills Ruining the Blanket</li>\n    <li>FUN DESIGN - Encourages Creativity and Imagination</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/usurper-products/72116/3vPEUJ3rjRQTeIa4d5L6mMcEdDXGGf-metaZmxlZWNlX2JsYW5rZXRfdmFyLmpwZw==-.jpg\" alt=\"Add some flair to your child&#039;s bedroom with the Officially Licensed Fleece Throw Blanket\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>Size:</strong> 45 in x 60 in</li>\n    <li><strong>Color:</strong> Multicolor</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>This super-soft throw blanket is made of 100% polyester, making it ideal for home decor, travel, picnics or beach parties. Easy to clean, this blanket is machine washable so you don&#039;t need to worry about occasional messes or spills ruining the blanket.</p>\n  <p>The throw blanket measures 45&quot; x 60&quot;, which is the perfect size for a child&#039;s bed, your favorite chair or as decor for a playroom or family room.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
